abstract: MySpace was once the pre-eminent social networking site, but recently it has lost some luster to Facebook.
snippet: MySpace was once the pre-eminent social networking site, but recently it has lost some luster to Facebook.
lead_paragraph: The latest step in Rupert Murdoch’s effort to turn around the fortunes of his digital businesses came Tuesday in the form of hefty layoffs at MySpace.

headline.main: MySpace Set to Lay Off 400 Workers
headline.print_headline: MySpace Set To Lay Off 400 Workers
